        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
        Webhook Rules - Config-Driven Event Tracking
        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
        
        These rules replace the old webhook.mixin inheritance system.
        Each rule defines:
        - Which model to track
        - Which operation (create/write/unlink)
        - Priority and category
        - Subscribers to notify
        
        Benefits:
        - No duplicate events
        - Better performance
        - Easy to manage from UI
        - No code changes needed per model
        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
        -->

